        <td style="padding:0 20px">
          <p style="padding-top:10px">Hi {{firstName}},</p>
          <p>We’re thrilled to see that you’ve registered to attend XDS 2025 in Vancouver. It’s going to be an action packed event, and we can’t wait to see you there.</p>
          <p>As a bonus for attending XDS, you receive a <b>complimentary 6-month Premium trial</b> of XDS Spark!</p>
          <p>Use Spark in the lead-up to XDS to see who’s attending, and determine who you would like to meet with while you’re on site. And/or discover new partners for upcoming projects.</p>
          <p>Click <a href="{{webSiteLoginUrl}}"><u>HERE</u></a> to access the log-in page. Your email is {{email}}, and your password is {{password}}</p>
          <p>Once you are logged in, here are a few tips to help you get started.</p>
          <ul>
            <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;"><b>Discover Service Providers -</b> View complete Service Provider profiles including portfolios, project highlights, certification and due diligence info, and contact partners as needed.</li>
            <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;"><b>Create Lists -</b> Build lists of Service Providers any way you want, and track and maintain these over time. Share lists with colleagues who are outside of Spark.</li>
            <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;"><b>Add Team Members -</b> As a Premium member, you can assign up to four (4) licenses to to your team members, and manage these accounts. Go to “Company Admin” in the navigation menu to get started!</li>
            <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;"><b>Post Opportunities -</b> Use Post Opportunities to share an upcoming project in order to discover new Service Provider candidates. Your post can be <b>anonymous</b>, and will only be published to Service Providers whose skills match that of your needs.</li>
            <li><b>Manage Partner Relationships</b> - Inside a Service Provider profile, go to the <b>My Spark</b> tab to manage personalized information that <u>only you can see</u>.</li>
            <ul>
              <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;" type="circle"><b>Partner Status -</b> indicating the service provider’s ability to work with your company</li>
              <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;" type="circle"><b>Rates -</b> track day and monthly rates by service with notes, and post a rate card</li>
              <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;" type="circle"><b>Performance -</b> track project performance by quality, on-time delivery and communication</li>
              <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;" type="circle"><b>Notes -</b> Post notes from meetings, or other important information on your partners</li>
            </ul>
          </ul>
          <p>Have questions, or need more info?  <a href="mailto:info@xds-spark.com?subject=General Inquiry" target="_blank"><u>Contact Us</u></a>, or check out our website at <a href="{{websiteUrl}}"><u>xds-spark.com</u></a>.</p>
          <p>Enjoy your Spark account, and see you at XDS 2025!</p>
